044package org.jfree.data.xy;
045
046/**
047 * Represent a data set where Y is a symbolic values. Each symbolic value is
048 * linked with an Integer.
049 */
050public interface YisSymbolic {
051
052    /**
053     * Returns the list of symbolic values.
054     *
055     * @return The symbolic values.
056     */
057    String[] getYSymbolicValues();
058
059    /**
060     * Returns the symbolic value of the data set specified by
061     * {@code series} and {@code item} parameters.
062     *
063     * @param series  the series index (zero-based).
064     * @param item  the item index (zero-based).
065     *
066     * @return The symbolic value.
067     */
068    String getYSymbolicValue(int series, int item);
069
070    /**
071     * Returns the symbolic value linked with the specified {@code Integer}.
072     *
073     * @param val  value of the integer linked with the symbolic value.
074     *
075     * @return The symbolic value.
076     */
077    String getYSymbolicValue(Integer val);
078
079}
